OS Assignment #5 v1.0

This is a program that share resources among processes with memory map. This program send unix signal to other proesses when data is changed.

This is run at ubuntu linux.

person.h
	In here, definition of data structures.
person.c
	In this file, modify or print value of data structure which is mapped in file using memory map. When user use -s option while runtime, user can change value of attibute. The additional funtion of this file for assignment is -w option that when other process's attribute have changed, this proess accept signal and print changed attribute and pid of process that send signal.

MakeFile
	A file that help control program files.
